! How To Connect To QMX+ Firmware on ~MacOS

* Select from the Shell menu of Terminal: New Window/Pro (Pro gets you color, apparently)
 
* Enable Control-S and Control-Q  (you need Control-Q to exit menus): ''stty -ixon -ixoff''
 
* To show connected ports: ''ls /dev/cu.*''
 
* To connect (use port name from above): ''screen /dev/cu.usbmodem1101''
 
* Then press enter to get Diagnostics menu.

https://groups.io/g/QRPLabs/message/127350

