!QMX Modes

DIGI:  Modulations that run in QMX/QMX+ DIGI mode :

* RTTY, AMTOR, PACTOR, HF Packet (300 baud)
* All WSTJ-x modes (FT8, FT4, JTxx, JS8Call, etc.), except MSK144
* In FLDIGI:
** Hellscriber: Feld Hell, but not the other Hell modes
** MFSK modes
** RTTY modes
** Olivia modes

SSB: Modulations that require SSB mode (almost all use upper-sideband) - don't forget to set the SSB input to the computer/USB interface

* all modes not mentioned above, eg:
* all PSK and QPSK modes
* all SSTV modes
* WSJT-x MSK144 mode
* all FLDIGI modes except those noted above

